* Used in [[retconned]] backstory for ''[[The Punisher (2004 film)|The Punisher]]'' (2004)
* The [[Bollywood]] movie [[Airlift (film)|Airlift]] (2016) is based on the [[1990 airlift of Indians from Kuwait|true story]] of the evacuation of 170,000 Indians stranded in the War Zone.
{{refend}}

